you are free ( german : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; frei ) is a 1983 west german short documentary film directed by dea &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , in which five former u.s. servicemen and a prison camp survivor give accounts of the liberation of the nazi concentration camps in 1945 . it was nominated for an academy award for best documentary short .